          "id": "nb_1783270408085_khfm_c0",
          "title": "Chapter 1",
          "text": "{{DCAT}} Check-in {{Introduction}}\nThe {{following}} {{policies}} and {{procedures}} {{require}} your {{attention}}.\nPlease take note of the {{signage}}. :\n* No {{personal}} items, bags, {{backpacks}}, or non-{{approved}} {{DBDs}} or f\n{{USB}} cables are {{{{allowed}} in}} areas {{such as}} colos, data halls, {{TN}}\n{{Welcome}} {{availability}} zones ({{AZs}}), {{information}} {{technology}} pre-{{assembled}} Es\n{{components}} ({{ITPACs}}), main {{distribution}} frames ({{MDFs}}), secure\n{{storage}}, high value asset and {{staging}} areas. |\nBadge and return it before {{leaving}} the site. i | a\nIf the person’s {{DCAT}} has {{approved}} {{photography}} {{permissions}}, state:\n¢ {{Explain}} their {{specific}} {{photography}} {{permission}} levels. I |\n{{Photography}} | If the person does not have {{photography}} {{permissions}}, state:\n{{Permissions}} ¢ You do not have {{photography}} {{permissions}} and are not {{permitted}} | {\nto take {{photographs}}, {{includes}} all videos, audio, video {{recording}}, | ad\n{{including}} live {{streaming}}, still images, and still-image {{recording}}. i\nIf the person’s {{DCAT}} has mobile {{permissions}} {{refer to}} {{section}} 10.5,\nMobile {{Patrolling}} on foot.\n{{equipment}} | If the person does not have mobile {{equipment}} {{permissions}}, state: |\n{{permissions}} e You do not have mobile {{permissions}} to take mobile {{equipment}} ii !\ninto the {{production}} {{environment}}. ; 0\ne The door policy at this {{facility}} is {{one swipe one entry}}. |\no Always {{wait for}} the door to close, then swipe your badge. i\no Ifthe card reader {{flashes}} green, you may {{proceed}}.\no Ifthe card reader {{flashes}} red, you do not have access and\nmay not enter.\no Do not allow anyone to enter a door unless they have\n5 {{completed}} the {{mentioned}} {{process}} or are being {{escorted}} in\nReine, {{accordance}} with the escort policy.\nNe ent. o Do not open or push on any {{emergency}} exit door unless an\npolicy {{emergency}} exists. Always use the main door to enter and\nexit spaces.\ne Escort policy (if {{applicable}}): |\no {{Escorted}} {{individual}}(s) must remain under the direct |\n{{supervision}} of the {{assigned}} escort {{at all times}}. ; | | |\no The {{escorted}} {{individual}} must follow all {{instructions}} |\n{{provided}} by the {{assigned}} escort while under escort. |\ne Your {{DCAT}} {{expires}} at [{{HH}}:{{MM}}] hours. : |\nbCal eo If you {{encounter}} any issues, come back to the {{security}} office, or\n{{expired}} call (—— | |",
          "myNote": ""
        }
      ],
